Class/Bits version 0.02
=======================

Class::Bits create class wrappers around bit vectors for easy access
to the bit fields inside then.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    Test::More

